I play a couple of online PvP games. Quake, CS, Jedi Knight, EQ pvp and the good news is that we're moving away from griefing. Sure you get some of the idiots ( we're seeing a few in this post aren't we? ) who want to spoil it for others but more and more we're seeing people tired of griefers firing up their own servers with the intent of creating a fair environment. <br>
<br>
Tossers like this who want to take the easy way aren't welcome in most of these places but unfortunately places like the arena on public servers will always have it. <p><CENTER><A HREF="http://ak.lonelygamer.com">
